casebody.data:
Joseph MILUTIN, Plaintiff,
and
Robert Healey, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
State of New Jersey, DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, Defendant-Respondent. C-551 September Term 2018
082056 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 28, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003387-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
